OL,4,Cmemorial
OL,6,FDeliberately located at the most
OL,7,Feasterly part of the Arboretum where
OL,8,Fthe sun rises first, the memorial was
OL,9,Finstalled in 2001 and contains 309
OL,10,Fwooden stakes to represent each
OL,11,Fsoldier.
OL,13,FThe memorial has suffered repeated
OL,14,Fdamage over the years due to flooding
OL,15,Ffrom the adjacent River Tame.
OL,17,FIt's hoped the funds raised can help
OL,18,Freplace the 309 wooden stakes with a
OL,19,Fmore durable, recycled material.
